               <lb xml:id="p003_tr_1_tl_5"/>Par l'URSS 
               <lb xml:id="p003_tr_1_tl_6"/>Le 2/2, 1) 
               <lb xml:id="p003_tr_1_tl_7"/>Monsieur Claude Bourdet 
               <lb xml:id="p003_tr_1_tl_8"/>47, Av. de Jéna 
               <lb xml:id="p003_tr_1_tl_9"/><hi rendition="#u">Paris</hi> 
               <lb xml:id="p003_tr_1_tl_10"/>FRANCE</p>

